{"id":100849,"date":"2018-02-28T08:00:29","date_gmt":"2018-02-28T13:00:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/techvibes.com\/?p=100849"},"modified":"2018-02-27T18:33:22","modified_gmt":"2018-02-27T23:33:22","slug":"killer-spaces-bluecat-toronto","status":"publish","type":"magazine","link":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-bluecat-toronto","title":{"rendered":"BlueCat&#8217;s Tranquil Toronto Treehouse"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>You can\u2019t always get what you want. Sometimes, you get something better. And sometimes, it&#8217;s a multi-million dollar idea. For the founders of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bluecatnetworks.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">BlueCat<\/a>, that\u2019s exactly what happened.<\/p>\n<p>In 1993, Michael and Richard Hyatt founded\u00a0Dyadem International, a risk management software company.\u00a0While researching a new DNS (domain name system), Richard created an interface that could install a server in five minutes\u2014a fraction of the complex, expensive two-day method that was standard at the time. They took one look at what was in front of them and knew it was a business opportunity.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">BlueCat was born in 2000 with both brothers at the helm. That interface became an early version of what the company offers today: trademarked DNS products that allow enterprises to manage their networks with ease.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103088\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Headquartered in Toronto, the Hyatts didn\u2019t start BlueCat with any venture capital or external funding.\u00a0That\u00a0bootstrapping mentality held until they were acquired <a href=\"https:\/\/borndigital.com\/2017\/02\/23\/bluecat-networks-acquired-by-madison-dearborn-partners-for-400-million\" target=\"_blank\">in 2017 for\u00a0$400 million<\/a> by the U.S. private equity giant Madison Dearborn Partners.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, while the Hyatts are no longer on the management team, they are well-known in the Canadian technology community as both investors and mentors. Michael continues to sit on the company\u2019s board of directors, while a different Michael\u2014Michael Harris\u2014serves as CEO and oversees nearly 380 employees.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Today, BlueCat works with companies who want to focus on business transformation and growth. Companies like Facebook, Disney, Sony, Apple, Nike, and J.P. Morgan\u2013to name a few.<\/p>\n<p><b>Work<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In September 2017, BlueCat moved into a new 38,000-square-foot, single floor office to house their growing team. With nearly 250 employees in Toronto alone, they wanted an open-but-functional workspace and worked alongside <a href=\"http:\/\/www.interiorarchitects.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Interior Architects Inc.<\/a> to realize their vision.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103095\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-8-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103092\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-730x487.jpg 730w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1460x973.jpg 1460w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Despite the busy office park location at Yonge and Highway 401, the BlueCat office backs onto an unassuming golf course. Not only does this provide tranquil views, it also makes the office extremely accessible for every team member. Each BlueCat works from collaborative spaces near their department leader\u2014each with their own sit-to-stand desk.\u00a0Each department\u2013known as pods\u2013has designated tablespaces for teamwork and white-boarding sessions, all\u00a0designed to encourage better brainstorming and more innovation.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103094\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-7-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakout spaces and call rooms are often used to change up work environments and find some quiet time, while the common area allows for informal meetups.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103104\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bluecat pulled the nature\u00a0into the office with tree-themed meeting rooms like Maple, Hawthorn and Willow.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103103\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103106\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103091\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>Food<\/b><\/p>\n<p>How many coffee beans do you really want to choose from in the morning? Six. Six is the correct answer for BlueCat and is the number of options at the cafe from the likes of\u00a0Starbucks, Balzac&#8217;s, Pilot Roasters, and more. The 3,000 square foot\u00a0<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">caf\u00e9 serves subsidized breakfasts and lunches with options that cater to every dietary restriction and preference. The lunch menu is the star of the show with a rotation of vendors including Z-Teca and Ma-Ro.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103099\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The dining space is furnished with reclaimed wood tables underneath beehive-inspired drop lights.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103096\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103097\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fridges are kept stocked with\u00a0complimentary drinks, while each team maintains their own snack table full of goodies. And, of course, the keg is always cold to help celebrate BlueCat wins.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103101\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The gaming lounge is central to the dining space, complete with a 60-inch television and three gaming consoles, just waiting for\u00a0challengers to be called into action for some post-lunch domination.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103098\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>Culture<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There\u2019s no shortage of team spirit here. BlueCat maintains five core values, both in their culture and on the wall\u2014collaboration, curiosity, clarity, transparency, and ownership.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103108\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>In addition to these values, new hires must also distinguish themselves with three key qualities: discovery, differentiation, and courage. Over the course of the year, twenty employees are recognized for embodying these principles.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103102\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103107\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095652\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-20-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The balance is real at BlueCat with wellness perks like free massages, on-site flu clinics, open exercise classes, subsidized gym memberships, and a generous vacation allowance.<\/p>\n<p>Every first week of April, the company hosts an annual event which sees all 100 offsite employees travel to Toronto. This is the biggest celebration of the year filled with product demos, team building, training sessions and the annual sales awards dinner honoring the top 10 sellers with a trip to an all-inclusive resort\u2013just in case Toronto gets a little cold.<\/p>\n<p>BlueCat operates a global charity called the CareCats. In 2017, the charity raised $82,000 for the Princess Margaret Cancer Centre through various community-centric fundraising initiatives\u2013bake sale anyone? Other efforts include clothing drives and fundraisers for charities based in Toronto.<\/p>\n<p><b>Education<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">BlueCat also gives their employees up to $1,000 each year from their own Continuing Education Fund to take programs and courses. If they don&#8217;t have that kind of time, BlueCat provides educational workshops and numerous off-topic lunch-and-learns on everything from mindful eating to financial wellness.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103100\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095654\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103090\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2.jpg\" alt=\"BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/01\/13095656\/BlueCat-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-2-1024x682